text:
Tempat : BnB Hotel Jakarta
Tanggal : 04 Ferbuari’16~8 Ferbuary’16

04 Ferbuari’16
Saya tiba di hotel (BnB Hotel Jakarta) tanggal 4 Ferbuari malam.
Saya check in dan masuk kamar (pertama kali bertemu karyawan hotel / pencuri )
Pertama Saya cek peti besi
Tapi tidak bisa pakai, dikarenakan peti besi rusak.
Saya cuma kunci pintu dan tidur.
Uangnya saya simpan di tas.
Tas saya letakkan di atas meja dan saya tidur.

05 Ferbuari’16
Pagi saya pergi ke restoran.
Karyawan hotel(Pencuri) cek saya keluar kamar dan masuk kamar saya dua kali (Udah cek CCTV)
Karyawan Hotel(Pencuri) masuk kamar menggunakan master key.
Pertama masuk di kamar saya selama 8 menit (CCTV) 
Kedua masuk di kamar saya selama 5 menit (CCTV)
Setelah saya selasai makan pagi, saya complain ke front desk.
Saya bicara peti besi rusak dan tidak bisa pakai.
Orangnya bicara tunggu kamar saja, Nanti orangnya datang.
Dan Dia bicara engak bisa pakai otometic, pakai manual dan dia kasih kuncinya.
Saya tidak cek uang saya dan uang langsung saya masukkan peti besi.(Uang sudah di curi)
Saya keluar hotel dan kembali lagi malam.
Saya tidak hitung uang Karena uangnya sudah saya simpan di peti besi.
Dan Saya tidur.

06 Ferbuari’16
Pagi saya pergi lagi ke restoran hotel.
Karyawan Hotel (pencuri) cek saya keluar dan masuk lagi kamar saya(Udah cek CCTV)
Saya selesai makan pagi dan kembali ke kamar.
Saya buka pintu dan terkejut, Karena Karyawan hotel(pencuri) ada di dalam kamar saya.
Saya Tanya karyawan hotel(pencuri) tersebut, Kenapa masuk kamar saya?
Karyawan hotel(pencuri) tersebut bicara cek kamar.
Karyawan hotel(pencuri) keluar kamar dan Saya ambil kunci dan buka peti besi (Kuncinya saya simpan di tas)
Saya coba hitung uang dan ternyata uang saya berkurang.
Uang saya hilang Rp.600.000, dan $ 600 dollar.
Saya terkejut dan terus pergi ke front desk dan cek CCTV
Karyawan hotel(pencuri) tiga kali masuk kamar saya.
Satu kali bertemu saya di kamar dan karyawan hotel(pencuri) kaget melihat saya.

Staff Hotel (Mieka) bicara, hari ini saya tidak di perbolehkan pergi ke Jogja.
DiKarenakan harus pergi bersama ke kantor polisi.
Saya jawab Ok, langsung cancel pasawat dan rental mobile (sudah bayar).
Pertama Mieka(staff hotel) bicara tidak bisa bantu lagi beli tiket pasawat dan rental mobile.
Saya komplain Mieka dan Dia bisa bantu.

06 Ferbuari’16 sore
Sore saya pergi ke kantor polisi dengan orang staff
Untuk buat document.
Ada satu orang saksi, Dia BnB hotel penjaga.
Dia datang dan bicara kepada polisi untuk buat laporan.
Dia bicara kalau karyawan hotel(pencuri) punya uang banyak.
Karyawan hotel(pencuri) punya uang $300 dollar dan Dia lihat tanggal 4 februari’16 sore.

Saya berfikir, orang saksi bagus (ada orang saksi dan proses cepat selesai).
Saya tinggal 4 jam di kantor polisi.
Saya pulang karena Saya takut kehilangan uang lagi dan sisa uang saya simpan di front desk.
Saya mau ganti kamar, Saya terkejut sudah Ganti kamar tapi peti besi tetap tidak bisa pakai.
Peti besi rusak seperti kamar yang lama.
Saya tidak komplain karena uang sudah sya simpan di front desk. 
Hari itu saya tidur lagi di BnB hotel.

7 Ferbuari’16
Siang pertama kali saya bertemu manager hotel(Bogank Serpiyadi).
Saya bicara kembalikan uang saya yang hilang tapi dia jawab tidak bisa sekarang.
Selesai proses polisi dulu dan uang kembali.
Saya tidak mengerti BnB hotel tapi saya tidak bisa tinggal lama di hotel tersebut.
Saya mau buat dokumen dan berangkat ke jogja.
Dia jawab ok dan buat janji di dokumen dan dia tanda tangan.

8 Ferbuary’16
Pagi saya berangkat ke bandara.
Saya mau pakai mobile hotel BnB.
Tp Mieka(orang staff) bicara tidak bisa karena mobile BnB baru sibuk.
Dia bicara pakai taxi aja tapi tidak bisa bantu uangnya.
Saya ok dan pakai taxi. Saya bayar taxi.
Saya pergi ke Jogja.

Saya tinggal di jogja Ferbuari.
Saya banyak bicara whatsapp dengan Mieka(orang staff)
Dia janji masalahnya bisa selesai Februari. (Ada bukti Whatsapp messeger)

Dia bicara uang bisa kembali tapi tunggu lagi dua minggu.
Saya ok dan tunggu lagi.

29 Ferbuari’16 
Saya kembali ke Korea
Saya tunggu dua minggu lagi.
Tapi uang saya belum juga kembali.
Saya komplain lagi Bogank dan Mieka.
Bogank bicara maunya dia, 50% kembali uang 50% hotel voucher

title: Karyawan Hotel(Pencuri) masuk kamar menggunakan master key dan curi uang.

text:
Lokasi hotel cukup dekat dengan mall (MOI, MKG), tapi untuk naik angkutan umum harus sedikit berjalan ke jalan besar.
Hotelnya sendiri sebenarnya cukup artistik, namun pengalaman saya kurang menyenangkan:
1. Pada saat check in, staff kurang ramah dan sibuk mengurus yang lainnya sehingga waktu check in cukup lama
2. Saya mendapatkan kamar dengan pengait kunci pintu copot, ketika saya melapor ke resepsionis, awalnya mereka tidak mau mengganti (dikunci biasa saja mba), saya agak ngotot karena kalau kunci biasa orang hotel yang mempunyai keycard bisa masuk dengan mudah. Akhirnya diganti juga kamarnya
3. Kamar penggantinya OK. Kekurangannya hanya handuk yang sangat kusam.
Masalah dimulai ketika jam 4 pagi tiba-tiba telpon kamar berdering. Deringan pertama saya diamkan sampai mati, eh ada telpon lagi, dan ketika saya angkat tidak ada suaranya. Saya menelpon resepsionis melaporkan hal ini, dan telpon saya tidak berbunyi lagi, tapi sayup sayup dari jauh ada suara telpon di beberapa kamar yang berdering-dering tidak diangkat, sampai 2x siklus dering seingat saya.

Keesokan harinya ketika saya tanya resepsionis, mereka tidak tahu apa-apa dan berterimakasih atas infonya.

Untuk harga yang saya bayarkan sepertinya lebih banyak pilihan lain yang lebih baik.

text:
Hotel budget yang terletak di daerah Kelapa Gading menjadi venue untuk acara rapat kerja akhir tahun perusahaan tempat saya bekerja. Saya akan mengulas tentang kamar, ruang meeting, dan makanan yang disediakan oleh pihak hotel selama acara berlangsung. 
Kamar dengan desain minimalis dan cukup luas, di sudut dekat wastafel terdapat debu pada skirting lantai yang menonjol. Saat kami check-in tidak ada botol air mineral compliment, dan sandal. Handuk yang disediakan pihak hotel juga terlihat kotor. 
Ruang meeting sudah ok, sangat disayangkan untuk mencapai ruang meeting ini harus melewati area parkiran dulu. Toilet ruang meeting kotor dan bau, tempat sampah juga tidak dikosongkan pada keesokan harinya, yang menyebabkan bau yang menyengat.
Makanan yang disediakan, baik itu saat coffe break, sarapan, makan siang, dan makan malam, sangat tidak enak. 
Dilihat dari segi harga per malam, saya merasa tidak sepadan dengan uang yang dikeluarkan.

Ukuran kamar cukup oke, toileteries hanya ada handuk, tidak ada keset, sehingga lantai bisa basah hingga ke kamar. Secara keseluruhan cukup oke sesuai dengan harganya.

Akses dengan kendaraan umum cukup  mudah, dengan busway ke arah tg priok & turun di halte sunter kelapagading & disambung angkot biru ke arah kelapagading turun di lottemart kelapagading & disambung jalan ke dalam sekitar 300 meter. Suasana kamar luas, rate semalam cukup wajar (sekitar Rp 400-500rban) namun akan sangat mahal jika book On line di rocketmile. Fasilitas kamar cukup dengan AC kencang, tv lega & siaran internasional, kamar mandi bersih, wifi kencang. Reception ramah. title: Cukup nyaman

text:
Saya sudah 3x menginap di hotel ini bersama pasangan dan terakhir menginap di tanggal 16-19 Juli 2015 selama 4 hari 3 malam.

Pertama kali saya menginap, saya merasa hotel ini memang bagus dengan design interior kamar yang cukup unik (westafel ada di luar kamar mandi). Yang paling menarik, anda pasti akan "sedikit" kebingungan untuk mencari tempat sampah di kamar Anda :D
Kali kedua dan ketiga, saya tidak merasakan improvement apapun baik dari pelayanan maupun fasilitas (tetap bagus seperti pertama saya menginap). Mungkin bisa lebih diperhatikan lagi untuk pelanggan yang sudah sering menginap, agar diberikan pelayanan ekstra (at least kalau sering menginap, berarti kita menganggap bahwa hotel Anda nyaman dan layak untuk menginap seterusnya)

Kelebihan :
1. Pelayan bagus dan cukup ramah dari para staf
2. Design kamar yang unik dan membuat cozy
3. Caffe yang cukup nyaman dan makanannya cukup enak (harga sedikir mahal)
4. Pelayanan receptionist yang 24 jam siaga.

Yang perlu di-improve :
1. TOLONG biasakan sediakan 2 pasang sandal hotel ! Ini saya Caps lock karena sudah 3x saya menginap tetapi tetap hanya ada 1 pasang.
2. Perbanyak jaringan TV kabel
3. Jaringan WIFI perlu dipercepat lagi
4. Kamar tolong lebih diperkedap ! karena saya sering terganggu apabila ada penghuni lain yang menutup pintu dengan keras, terutama apabila ada anak kecil yang berlarian di lorong !
5. Mohon lebih cepat dalam mengantarkan sesuatu ke dalam kamar
6. Lantai lift dapat diperbaiki karena ada beberapa yang retak-retak

Kekurangan :
Hari terakhir saya menginap (19 Juli 2015) saya dan pasangan merasa sedikit kecewa dengan room service Anda, karena mereka masuk dan membersihkan kamar saya tanpa saya minta ! Dimana banyak barang-barang privacy dan barang berharga yang saya tingga di kamar ! Mohon diperhatikan dengan sangat !

Demikian sedikit ulasan dari saya, semoga dapat segera ditindak lebih lanjut.
title: Worth It !! Perlu tingkatkan pelayanan demi kepuasan customer !

text:
Hotel ini terletak di daerah kelapa gading dan berada cukup masuk ke dalam dari jalan raya. Secara tampilan luar, hotel ini terlihat biasa saja dan ketika masuk agak modern. Liftnya sedikit perlu dipercantik dan diperhatikan kebersihan dan wangi-nya. Untuk kamar kita mendapat lokasi yang jauh dari lift dan kamarnya seperti ukuran smart hotel yang standar, kamar tidak terlalu besar. One thing yang kurang, tidak adanya keset di dalam kamar, di mana perlu diperbaiki. Lanjut ke breakfast, makanan cukup OK, hanya pilihan tidak terlalu banyak.

Overall, untuk smart hotel cukup ok namun perlu sedikit improvement.
title: Hotel Modern Nan Minimalis

text:
4juni 2015 kami menginap,krna ada keperluan disekitar kelapagading. Kamar sempit kecil, tdk ada coffe maker,kulkas/minibar, kamarmandi licin, kamar kurang terang (saya kesulitan bekerja dikamar),meja kecil banget dgn 1 kursi. Tdk ada gantungan/lemari utk baju. Sandal hotel 1, kita nginap kan berdua?? saat masuk kamar saya mengeluh krna ac tdk dingin,teknisi kemudian memeriksa dan bisa dingin. Banyak suara aneh dikamar yg cukup mengganggu, batas kamar jg terlalu tipis tampaknya, suara wanita mengerang kamar sebelah terdengar dari kamar saya.

Sarapan ala kadarnya. Nasi uduk,tempe kering,ikan tepung prasmanan. Tdk ada yg spesial menurut saya. Tdk ada minum dingin atau es. Layanan lambat. Chef pembuat omelet tdk ditempat. Omelet asin bgt. 

Plusnya wifi cepat,parkir mudah, satpam ramah, lokasi strategis.

Oya hotel menerapkan deposit 100rb, entah buat apa? Minibar ga ada, deposit? 

Saya tdk akan datang lagi untk ke 2x nya. Harga yg ditawarkan tdk rasional dan sebanding dgn layanan/fasilitas yg saya dapatkan. Sebaiknya manajemen memperhatikan keluhan ditripadvisor utk perbaikan,krna apa yg saya alami sdh dialami pengunjung sebelum saya.

text: Lokasi cukup strategis namun sulit untuk mencari Restarant yang dekat dengan berjalan kaki, sedangkan terlalu dekat apabila naik taksi. text:
Hotel BnB yang terletak di uatara Jakarta ini tepatnya di daerah Kelapa Gading sangatlah cocok untuk dijadikan refrensi anda untuk menerima tamu kantor. tidak hanya pelayanan yang ramah, namun suasana modern minimalis sangat terlihat dalam desain ruangan.
Harga relatif cukup terjangkau dan murah jika disertai fasilitas dan kenyamanan yang disediakan disana. menu breakfast bisa dikatakan cukup memanjakan lidah, omletnyapun enak, ruangan bersih dan cukup luas.
disekitar hotel terdapat banyak sekali pusat perbelanjaan yang bisa ditempuh dengan jalan kaki ataupun menggunakan angkot dan kendaraan pribadi.
lokasi hotel juga dekat dengan beberapa Mall Besar di Jakarta Utara yang cukup terkenal antaralain Mall Artha Gading( Mall Seribu Satu Malam ), MOI ( Mall of indonesia ), MKG (Mall Kelapa Gading ) dan tempat tongkrongan LA Piazza..
selain itu didaerah ini banyak sekali refrensi resto yang dapat dikunjungi untuk menambah cita rasa kuliner anda.
untuk itu saya katakan bahwa hotel ini sangat bagus untuk dijadikan tempat refrensi tamu anda dalam bisnis dan tugas dinas.
title: Hotel Refrensi untuk Tamu Kantor

text:
lokasi agak jauh dari pusat perbelanjaan.

title: kurang memuaskan

text:
The bnb hotel memiliki kamar yang nyaman, dan sarapan dengan omelet yang enak sekali. Namun kekurangannya hotel ini kamar tidak terlalu kedap suara. Kamar mandi bersih, kamar bisa request dengan jendela, dan secara ukuran tidak sempit. 
Di sekitarnya, bnb hotel dekat dengan lotte mart, hanya saja harus jalan memutar untuk menemukan pintu masuknya. Jika ingin ke mall  harus menggunakan taksi, atau bisa jalan namun jauh dan tidak nyaman, akibat kondisi seputar yang sangat 'gated' .  Lokasi bnb hotel meskipun ada di tengah kelapa gading namun secara aksesibilitas untuk ke tempat2 makanan, dan mall tidak dalam jangkauan berjalan kaki. Letak hotel ini dekat dengan travel baraya, bisa berjalan kaki meskipun harus lewat belakang dan agak sedikit memotong jalan.
title: Kamar nyaman

text:
Waktu check in sedang ada perdebatan antara tamu hotel (atau pihak dr luar hotel) dengan manager (atau mungkin staff), terdengar si manager meminta maaf berulang kali, namun si tamu tetap marah dan ngedumel2...
Diminta deposit saat check in, kirain karna ada mini bar, ternyata takut electric key nya rusak/hilang (lumayan pelit), pintu kamar mandi berfungsi jg sebagai pintu lemari dengan cara digeser, jadi kalo anda mau keluar dari kamar mandi, pastikan tidak ada orang yg sedang dekat kamar mandi, atau dia bisa terluka..
Saat sarapan??? bagi saya yg bukan pemakan nasi, jam 8.30 sudah susah mendapatkan apa2, akhirnya saya sarapan sayur sawi putih ditambah omelet dengan rasa hambar, semua sudah habis...
saat akan mengambil air putih, gelasnya tidak ada, saya panggil staff nya untuk menyediakan gelas, tp cuek begitu saja. akhirnya setelah 10 menit disediakan gelas air putih yang baru saja dicuci tanpa di lap, dalam keadaan basah, diletakkan begitu saja.. what the..??
Enaknya sih lokasi strategis, ada shuttle ke MOI di jam tertentu, seafood ayu favorit saya tepat di belakang hotel, dekat dgn Balai samudera dan Lotte mart, dan beberapa tempat hiburan malam..
title: Strategis, namun saat sarapan yang mengecewakan....

text:
Hotel ini luar biasa lebih dari cukup kalau memang tujuan kamu nginep hanya untuk numpang tidur.
Dengan harga 400an ribu kamu udah dapet semua hal paling basic yang kamu harapkan dari sebuah penginapan di ibukota : tempat tidur dan bantal yang cukup ok - kamar mandi & toilet yang bersih - sikat gigi dan odol - air mineral. 
Walaupun posisi wastafel lumayan canggung (begitu buka pintu kamar langsung berhadapan dengan menara wastafel) tapi kamu dapat bonus wi-fi yang lumayan speednya, meja kerja yang lumayan lega untuk nulis-nulis atau berlaptop, tv kabel dan brankas loh!

Untuk urusan sarapan, standar banget tapi cukupanlah untuk ganjel perut sementara pagi-pagi. Lokasi lumayan oke. Di area Kelapa Gading yang terkenal dengan aneka restoran enak dan beberapa mall besar di Jakarta Timur. Akses menuju jalan tol pun lumayan dekat dan mudah plus hotel ini memiliki pool taxi. Ini penting karena di area ini cara transportasi utama adalah berkendara mobil.

Jadi untuk kamu yang beragenda shopping atau bisnis di area Kelapa Gading atau Jakarta Timur, bolehlah hotel ini masuk ke daftar kandidat.
title: Pas Untuk Agenda Shopping dan Bisnis

text:
Perpaduan warna merah dan putih pada eksterior dan interiornya menegaskan konsep minimalis modern pada hotel ini. Begitu memasuki pintu masuk kacanya yang berwarna merah, Anda akan disambut oleh petugas resepsionis yang berdiri sigap di depan latar putih bertuliskan, "Hello, there. Apa kabar?" Anda dapat memilih kamar dengan harga mulai dari Rp 325.000,00.

Selain resepsionis, lantai 1 ini juga difungsikan sebagai lounge, ruang makan, dan cafe "Kafein". Anda dapat bersantai di atas sofa merahnya yang empuk. Membaca surat-surat kabar yang sudah disediakan di atas meja panjang sambil menyaksikan televisi. Menikmati sarapan pagi dengan meja-kursi kayu berwarna merah dan putih.

Menu sarapan pagi yang disajikan adalah local cuisine, misalnya: fuyunghai, chicken black pepper, dan sayur-sayuran. Lengkap dengan roti, buah, dan kopi atau teh sebagai pilihan minum. Selesai sarapan, silakan membereskan sendiri piring - gelas Anda untuk mematuhi konsep self-clearing service yang diberlakukan. Sayangnya banyak penghuni yang tidak melakukan dan para petugas hotel tidak berani mengingatkan.

Resepsionis akan memberikan sebuah smart-card dan kertas berisi username + password untuk mengakses fasilitas wifi hotel. Jika Anda tidak membawa notebook sendiri, Anda bisa menggunakan ruang komputer hotel yang ada di samping resepsionis. Smart-card digunakan untuk membuka / menutup kamar hotel dan lift. Iya, lift. Jadi tidak akan ada penyelundup gelap yang bisa naik turun dengan lift. Ada bell boy yang akan mengantar Anda menuju kamar.

Kamar berisi dua buah ranjang kecil yang dilapisi sprei putih, diapit dua buah lampu berbentuk limas yang berpendar keemasan. Ada cermin untuk wastafel, tempat sampahnya ada di bawah meja wastafel. Total ada 3 colokan standar dan 1 colokan kaki tiga, dua di antaranya terletak di dekat meja kerja. Jadi nyaman banget kalau ada kerjaan. Kursinya empuk dan bisa diputar. Televisi layar datar dengan tangkapan yang tidak terlalu jernih menempel di dinding di atas meja kerja. Wifinya lancar.

Shower dan toilet dipisahkan dengan sekat. Sudah disediakan air minum, alat-alat mandi, handuk, keset, dan sendal. Air hangatnya berfungsi dengan baik dan tidak berlebihan.

Dengan karakteristik kamar seperti itu, saya dapat merumuskan hotel ini lebih didedikasikan untuk kalangan traveler, anak muda, dan pebisnis. Apalagi hotel ini terletak dekat dengan Mal Kelapa Gading, La Piazza, Mal Artha Gading, dan kawasan kuliner Kelapa Gading.
title: Hotel Budget yang Pas Untuk Business Trip

photos.caption: Tempat sampah ada di bawah wastafel

text:
Awal saya dtg, sepertinya saya berekspektasi berlebihan dengan hotel ini. Pelayanannya kurang. Nggak ada door-man yg menyambut dan membukakan pintu. Pdhl saat itu suasana cukup sepi. Di resepsionis hanya ada 2 petugas (laki2) yg melayani, no welcome greeting n no welcome drink. Proses check-in lumayan lama. Kunci kamar pun diserahkan. Dan saya berjalan sendiri ke lift dan kamar. Tidak ada petugas yg mengantarkan ke lift, apalagi ke kamar. Poor service.
However, I love the room. Furniturnya minimalis tp dengan fungsi maksimalis. Kamar tdk terlalu luas tp cukup lega untuk berdua. Wifi available in all area, helps me to keep connected around.
am i going to make another reservation here? Yes, only if you improve your service :)
title: Pay less, less service, sleep well.

text:
Bulan Agustus 2014, saya ada menginap di hotel ini beberapa kali. Selain harganya ekonomis, saya menyukai desain kamarnya yang minimalis yang membuat tidur semakin nyaman. Lokasi hotel ini sangat dekat ke Mall Of Indonesia dan Lottemart Kelapa Gading. Ingat, ada Shuttle Bus menuju MOI yang gratis. Sarapan tersedia, walaupun menunya sangat terbatas, tetapi diganti setiap hari. Hotel ini juga masih terkesan baru. Pelayanan counter desk juga ramah. Hotel ini wajib di coba, baik untuk urusan bisnis maupun rekreasi.
Sebagai tambahan, Hotel ini mempunyai cafe juga lho.
title: Hotel Stylish dengan Harga Ekonomis

text:
Pertama kali menginap di hotel ini, dari Bandara Soekarno Hatta kemudian melewati tol tanjung Priok dan turun di sunter kemudian menyusuri pinggir MOi dan setelah Lotte Mart belok Kanan. Lokasi hotel ini terletak di belakang Gading Marina dan sangat mudah ditemukan. Saya booking melalui telepon dan cek in dilakukan cepat, sebelumnya Jika anda menggunakan kartu kredit maka harga yang dibayar cukup murah dibanding dengan tunai, kamar hotel bersih dan rapi, suhu kamar cukup, handuk, sprei dan alat mandi cukup baik. Keunikan kamar terdapat wastafel didepan kamar mandi.

Sarapan pagi cukup bervariasi dengam kopi dan teh beserta air putih, saya tidak menemukan juice dll. Makanan cukup enak, dan untuk hotel budget sangat baik. 

Kesulitan adalah, kunci kamar yang hanya satu, dan untuk akses lift harus menggunakan kunci tersebut. sehingga jika turun naik harus membawa kunci tersebut. Koneksi wifi dalam kamar cukup kencang meskipun tidak terlalu cepat.

Dinding kamar cukup tipis sehingga terdengar suara dari luar dan samping kamar jika mengaktifkan televisi, hal tersebut cukup mengganggu jika anda ingin beristirahat dipagi hari setelah perjalanan jauh.
title: Harga ekonomis, kamar cukup luas, lokasi dekat Mall

text: Hotelnya cukup nyaman. Kamarnya kecil sesuai harga. yang agak merepotkan kunci hotel kamar(berbentuk kartu) hanya diberi satu, sehingga jika akan kembali ke kamar setelah dari parkiran mobil untuk mengambil/menaruh barang harus meminta bantuan resepsionis, karena kunci kamar berfungsi juga untuk akses lift menuju lantai kamar dan juga sebagai kunci penerangan kamar. Jadi kunci hotel(kartu) tidak bisa dicabut karena, jika dicabut kamar akan gelap.
title: BnB hotel kelapa gading

text:
sudah kesekian kalinya menginap di hotel ini karena selain murah, kamar tersedia cukup luas untuk ukuran hotel ekonmi.
makan pagi disediakan secara prasmanan.
hal menarik lainnya adalah lokasinya yang strategis di kelapa gading, mudah mencapai MOI ataupun pusat perbelanjaan lainnya.

text: Saya mendapat informasi dari kolega,bahwa the bnb hotel adalah hotel bintang 3 yang memiliki design interior yang bagus,ternyata benar,pengalaman saya waktu stay di hotel tersebut terbukti,bahwa designnya benar2 bagus,terutama interior kamarnya,mempunyai staff yang ramah,dan ternyata harga kamarnya tergolong murah,service sangat memuaskan,good hotel,sudah bagus dan terus tingkatkan

text: Pertama kali saya menginap disana untuk suasana tempat yang sangat nyaman dan untuk ruangan kamar pun juga nyaman dan bersih dan setiap harinya kalian akan slalu disambut dengan staf staf yang ramah. Dan karena  di daerah perkotaan maka untuk mencari sesuatu tidaklah sulit seperti pakaian atau pun belanja makanan dan taxi pun selalu stand by 24 jam di depan lobby.dan satu yang saya suka decorasi kamar yang minimalis membuat saya betah untuk berada dikamar
title: tempat yang nyaman dan strategis

text:
Saya mencoba Hotel BnB Kelapa Gading berdasarkan rekomendasi dari kolega bahwa hotel ini termasuk baru di kelapa gading untuk kelas bintang 3, seperti kebiasaan, saya akan melihat review dan website hotel dimana saya akan stay.

Dan akhirnya tanpa kesulitan dari bandara untuk mencapai hotel, untuk masuk ke lobby BnB Hotel anda akan memasuki Red Box, nama yang cukup keren tapi bisa membuat anda pusing karena cahaya merahnya, lebih baik ganti kaca merah dengan dinding merah saja.

Kesan pertama selanjutnya saat tiba di hotel ini adalah pelayanan yang buruk dari recepsionist, yah bukan ucapan salam yang saya terima tetapi adalah pertanyaan "ada apa?" dan tata cara penerimaan tamu yang tidak sesuai standar..dan akhirnya sempat saya memutuskan hanya menginap 1 malam dari 3 malam yang sudah saya reservasi, tidak ada room boy yang membawakan tas ke kamar, saya hanya berpikir untuk apa saya mencoba hotel baru tapi dengan pelayanan di front office saja sudah membuat bad mood.dan saat keluar dari lift, anda akan disambut udara panas di koridor menuju kamar hotel.

Saya memilih kamar tipe Urban Deluxe yang merupakan kamar tertinggi di hotel ini, impresi pertama saat memasuki kamar cukup bagus dan melegakan, yah dibandingkan sambutan di recepsionist hotel, kamar luas untuk ukuran bintang 3, dingin dan bersih dengan nuansa biru putih cukup membuat segar, meskipun plafon kamar rendah dengan gelagar di atas tempat tidur anda, jangan mencari jendela untuk memasukkan cahaya keruangan karena memang tidak ada hahaha...

Saya penasaran apakah saya mendapatkan kamar yang aneh saja dengan tidak adanya jendela di kamar, saya keluar dan coba membandingkan kamar lainnya, kebetulan saya berjumpa dengan house keeper yang ramah dan menunjukan kamar tipe standar..ternyata kamar standar jauh lebih cerah dan menarik dan dengan lay out ruang yang sama meskipun minus sofa, agak aneh bagi saya mengapa kamar deluxe kurang menarik dibandingkan kamar standar hehehehe...

Wastafel terletak di luar kamar mandi memang unik dan ini baru pertama saya lihat hanya saja gelas plastik dan sikat gigi yang dijadikan satu dengan sandal hotel adalah hal yang sangat aneh.

Kamar mandi bersih dan bagus dengan shower dan air panas yang cepat , dengan dinding kaca adalah hal yang unik juga, untuk kamar mandi tidak ada rak untuk meletakkan perlengkapan mandi pribadi, saya rasa hotel harus menyediakan rak !!, pintu kamar mandi geser adalah hal yang unsafe karena bergabung menjadi satu dengan rak lemari disebelah nya, apabila ada rekan/pasangan anda sedang meletakan sesuatu di lemari dan anda membuka pintu dijamin rekan/pasangan anda tertabrak pintu yang anda buka..hal kecil yang bisa membuat suasana menginap menjadi berantakan.

Kamar tidur dilengkapi dengan sofa besar dan TV beserta rak yang unik dan belakangnya adalah cermin besar...this is the best design. untuk kualitas tempat tidur saya kira bisa diimprove sama seperti hotel kompetitor.

Oke, selanjutnya penilaian terhadap sarapan pagi...hanya satu saja..it's BAD Breakfast, menu terbatas dan tidak menarik, anda mau mencari kopi atau teh silahkan ambil sendiri dengan gelas jadul ala warteg..jadi sarapan di BnB Hotel ini adalah yang terburuk dari hotel bintang 3 yang pernah saya coba untuk stay, seharusnya bisa di improve lebih baik termasuk model kursi dan meja makan nya.Tapi untuk ada coffeshop di hotel ini not bad..untuk lobby dengan kursi merahnya cukup bagus untuk duduk duduk.

Dan mengenai complain terhadap front office saya langsung sampaikan kepada salah seorang manager hotel sebelum saya meninggalkan hotel untuk urusan kerja, dan setiba di hotel saya coba test apakah sambutannya sama..ternyata saya mendapatkan sambutan yang ramah dari recepsionist yang berbeda, ramah dan well explained, dan menyampaikan maaf atas ketidak nyamanan sebelumnya..well this is a good improvement !, akhirnya saya memutuskan untuk tetap stay di hotel ini sesuai dengan reservasi saya, dan point penting, anda akan mendapatkan room rate yang lebih murah jika menginap lebih lama.

Lokasi hotel sendiri sangat strategis mudah ditemukan dan selangkah ke Mall Of Indonesia, jika ingin mencari makanan atau tempat kebugaran cukup banyak ditemukan di sekitar hotel, Taksi sangat mudah didapatkan dan pelayanannya cukup baik dan hanya butuh waktu sekitar 1 jam untuk mencapai bandara.

Tempat parkir kendaraan yang memadai, jika tidak cukup di halaman hotel masih ada space yang cukup aman di sekitar hotel.

fasilitas jaringan komputer dan wifi yang cepat dan gratis adalah point positif hotel ini.

Secara overall BnB Hotel termasuk hotel yang recommended, wajar sebagai hotel yang baru opening banyak hal yang harus diperbaiki baik dari sisi staff hotel dan fasilitas kamar, namun jika terdapat komplain atau masukan dari tamu tidak ditindak lanjuti maka mungkin hotel ini akan ditinggalkan tamunya.
title: Recomended Hotel di Area Kelapa Gading..tapi perlu ditingkatkan kualitasnya

text: Speedy internet for free, ample parking space and clean room, in the middle of Kelapa Gading, one of shopping destination in North Jakarta. The room provided no sandals, one set toothbrush and two clean towel. Overall worth the money, will definitely come back again
title: Worth the money

text:
First thing first...What I like about this hotel...The people is friendly and helpful, and this is not limited to the concierge & receptionist, but also to the security, room service, and other people working in the hotel. 

What I am quite disappointed with the hotel is the condition of the room. The room is reasonably clean, but the TV is off quite often due to the switchboard, the AC can't be adjusted, and I find the towel was rather dirty. I stayed in this hotel 2 years ago, and the room condition was great, and that's why I am so disappointed with the condition now.

In terms of location, it's not too far from Mal Kelapa Gading (maybe around 15 min by taxi), and Mall of Indonesia (MOI) - the hotel provides shuttle bus to this place.
Taxi is easy to get from the hotel.
title: Friendly people

text:
First time I checked in the concierge hospitality was super nice.

Second time it was super busy and the rate they offered was a bit higher than the last time. TV was not working that we had to wait for a technician to come. Neighbor can be really noisy sometimes, wall isn't that thick.

Location wise, pretty strategic as it's near Mall of Indonesia.
title: Nice area and hospitality

text:
Its my most favourite hotel ever.  The room was so cozy and it feels like home. But one thing which needs improvement here is their wifi, because its so slow... More terrible than my mobile operator.  

For the breakfast,  its so so.  Not too many varieties..  And for the bread,  they dont give toaster so we cant have toasted bread here.  But overall, its still acceptable.
title: Its Cozy and clean

text:
The TV in our room would not turn on, though it was because of the switchboard and not because the TV was broken. The aircon controls sometimes would be unresponsive.

The hotel accommodated our special requests like having separate beds instead of a queen size bed. The rooms were clean and the basic amenities were included (toiletries, tissues, slippers, toothbrush and toothpaste). The complimentary water was a really nice touch.
title: Value for money

text:
like the title i wrote
everything is average
small room, but amenities are quite enough
the smoking room floor is really for smokers only! because you can smell cigarette smokes right from the lift door is open lol

the good thing i found best is the free parking :)
title: average budget

text:
Was looking at great budget options around Kelapa Gading and found this hotel. Decided to book due to the location and price. First the good. For what you get the price is great. I booked the deluxe urban double bed and the room size was reasonable and functional.  It's reasonably clean and bed is comfortable   Breakfast is include. Very basic though so don't expect much. wifi is also free but connection is quite slow. 
There is no gym or swimming pool since this is a budget hotel. The shops and mall are a bit of a walk to get to but if you have a car it's easier. Overall a reasonable stay especially for the price point. So value for money.
title: Great option if on a tight budget

text:
We stayed here 2 nights. The room was simple, minimalistic but good enough. Shower was also ok. The location is also good, close to the MOI, the only thing is that it is quite hard to find. Maybe they should put some signage on the main road. The big minor was the breakfast. There was really a limited of choice and the quality of what was given was not good. This should really be upgraded. Also the choice of food and beverage was really limited. There is only something like a coffee shop, but there are no fresh drinks. Only a machine put away in a corner of the restaurant. There is also no information if there is room service available 24 hrs.
The staff was friendly and helpful From the security to the housekeeping. Everybody was helpful and polite. 
We had a good night sleep, the bed is good and that is one of the most important things.
title: Simple but enough

text: went to this hotel by the recomendation of my friend, its not like a hotel if u look from the outside it just looks like "pertokoan". but however it is located in a strategic area 5 minutes from MOI and 10 min from MKG. friendly staff. but the breakfast should be your consideration if u gonna stay in this hotel. its not good at all!
title: good hotel

text:
From outside this hotel appearance is good and minimalist.. The design is nice, the structure is average and kind a different.. I think because this hotel were build from old Mall that already bankrupt, so The management were adapting its old building structure..

The Check-in process is average, there's only one staff that handle all guest check-in process and its quite fast, its only took around 10 minutes for handling one guest.. The lobby ambiance is quiet even there's a coffee shop..

The room is small and I choose the double bed.. The design is quite good and simple.. The basin is outside of the bathroom.. its have shower, hot water available and its operate well.. They give two kind of towel, and its clean.. The TV channel however is poor because there's only a few movie channel.. The Bedding is nice, blanket available, the pillow is in good condition.. There's a safe in the room, and there's WiFi for free but the signal is really poor especially if you get the room that in the backside of hotel.. for a IDR 549.000 per night, this hotel is really worth the try..

My only complain is the breakfast section.. They provide coffee and Tea, but where's the creamer and sugar..?? they used a cup to get juices and water..?? where's the glass..?? The first day I'm having breakfast, there's employee with low neatness to dress.. He using Shirt that's not tuck in, and the shirt is not the same as the others, its not a uniform.. if He a training staff, why he doesnt wear standard training staff uniform (usually black & White).. If He is a supervisor or Manager, its worst that he dont pay attention in His grooming.. He working in a hospitality and services industry..

Overall is a good hotel with minor problem.. I still recommended this Hotel to all Traveller that need hotel in North Jakarta.. because its near Mall of Indonesia, ITC cempaka Mas, Kelapa Gading Mall, close to Airport toll..

My Valuation for this Hotel : C-
title: BUDGET OR BUSINESS HOTEL...???

text:
Stay for 7 days.

Room was neat and clean, also the hotel area, nice room ambience, complete with cable tv, perfect tv size.

The cons only the kaffein (restaurant/cafe) should open at least until 12am (its open until 9pm only), its not easy to find good food surround hotel area and place to hangout for coffee time with friends after 9pm, you can only reach good place for hangout by taxi, walking distance quiet far away from hotel.
And lack of soundproof, you stil can hear footstep from people walking at the hotel hallway and next from your room.

text:
First Impression.

The hotel itself is quite good despite the lobby, feels like entering the kind of spaceship.  
The staff at front office are helpful. And check in process done very fast and smooth.

Honestly the room is bigger than my expectation, especially i got the one in the corner, with more space. I would reccomend for walk in guest to ask for room 1027, 2027 (anyway, the room in the corner with more space).

The breakfast is so so. But i'm not complaining since the hotel rate is quite low, so i took it as acceptable.

The only one annoying in the hotel is the bathroom, there is no place for put your own amenities. So i need to put them on the toilet, my bathgel, shampoo, etc. And it is quite annoying experiences. And make the floor wet too, need to go here and there to get things.

So I would like to give strong reccomendation to the management to put some hanger on your shower area. A simple fit out will make away bad experiences. Cheers.

I will look for improvement on my next visit.
title: Good Budget Hotel. There are rooms for future improvement

text:
I have stayed in 3 budget hotels in the area (Fave, Whitz, and BnB) and Harris hotel, so far this is the best budget hotel in the area. It is located in a more quiet street but the location is close to shopping malls. It only takes 5-10 minutes to walk to MOI (Mall of Indonesia). The room is spacious and clean. The wifi connection is considerably good. 

Unlike other budget hotel in the area that was build inside an apartment complex or as a part of shopping complex, this hotel was build in its own land. It has plenty of space for parking your car. So, this hotel is perfect for guest who want to stay in budget hotel and bring their own car.
title: The Best Budget Hotel in the area so far

text:
The procedure applied for quarantine arrival package was really smooth. They provide another receptionist area to welcome the guests for quarantine purposes. 
Its located nearby the parking area, so will not disturb other guests who stay in this Hotel. 
The check-in process was also quick. They provide us clear information and guidance for 3 days staying at the Hotel.
Room space is enough, clean and also has a good lightings.
The foods was good. We also had a afternoon breakfast.

They also served a PCR test, 1 day before the check out.
The Nurse visit the room and do the PCR test inside the room.
Its safe for everyone.

Also we could use the laundry facility given (5pcs/day)

They also provide us the letter of clearance + lab result during check out, so we can show this to person in charge in the neighborhood. Showing that we already undergone quarantine as per the regulations.

Overall, its a pleasant stay! And will surely be back here..
Thank you.

Note: And one of the staff there, Pak Rifky was very helpful.
title: Pleasant quarantine stay for 3 days!

text: We stayed here for 10d quarantine and its the worst choice ever. The food is always the same everyday, chicken/Meat that is so hard and impossible to eat. I also got a little worm on one of my meal and when i called the reception, the response were "are you sure?" lol and they only sent a regular staff to apologize as it was nothing important. An hour later i called the reception again to ask if they just move on about it and then later they sent a Fruit platter with an ice cream. Well shouldn't be the manager come up for a proper apology and clarification, we CAN buy a plate of Fruit for goodness sake, but this treatment prove that the hotel didn't take guest's matter seriously. There is also NO privacy, i can hear the people who are in corridor as well as the guest who stays in the next room talking, like literally the Whole convos, i'm sure they also can hear our convos but again what can i do. The staff did blood pressure check at 9PM without any prior notice, 4 people just bang on the door while i was brushing my teeth and they did not even let me finish it, they just do their thing. And in general they always bang on the door with all their energy (not knocking) and they send breakfast at 6.30AM, i put the  DO NOT DISTURB sign at the doorknob but the staff ignored it and keep on banging the door for 5 DAYS until i explain to them: look i always put this sign and then He said sorry. When i called the front office for a scissors and a bowl, the receptionist told me to call directly to the restaurant for the bowl and TO TELL the restaurant staff to stop by the reception to pick up the scissors, the audacity the staff TOLD me to do things for them instead of him to call his colleague in the restaurant is so bad (plus they will charge you for borrowing a small bowl that will be useless which doesn't make sense). I also told them i don't have rupiah in cash as i came straight from airport so i asked them if they can put the bill in the room tab, the staff insisted it should be cash. So i cancelled but they sent the staff anyway.. When leaving the hotel, one of the reception staff run to me and asked if i took a picture of the rice with the WORM and asked me send it to his WhatsApp. WOW literally there is no good communication between them. Overall i would NEVER come back nor recommend this hotel. Save your money and go somewhere with better reputation, unless you want to ruin 10days of your life.

text:
Been here with friend and her children. The check in process is easy and the front desk staffs are very helpful. They provided clear explanation about the room which match with our needs. They even invited us to join their staff gathering for welcoming New Year eventhough you have to pay if you want to join the BBQ. Thank you for the invitation.

The room is quite comfy, it's just lack of lighting. It is bright at the room front area where you can find a washtafle but it is quite dark in sleeping area. There are only two dim lights table lamps. I got the sense that the hotel is built not for long period stay and It is good for business trip.

The cleanliness is quite good but there are some problems at the toilet. Maybe not all, but it was in my friend's room. The flushing and the bidet were trouble, but the staffs were quick to response. Thanks to that!

The location is quite easy to find if you know the area very well. It is located accross Lotte mart and luckily, its building is quite high with red color sign. For access, you need to call taxi. It is quite far from the main road.

Other facility is that they provide water dispense if you want to refill your bottle or cook pot noodle.

Overall, it is a nice hotel for business trip or short stay. Do not have the pictures as we're already tired for long trip and just need to rest.

Thank you for the service and the friendliness.
title: Nice service

text:
I was stay in this hotel from 21 - 23 Oct 2017. 
First check in was fast (didn’t like other customer comment). Perhaps because I have book few days before. When I check in the reception even didn’t tell me where the restaurant for me to have bfast and the elevator or even they didn’t escort me to my room. Well that was first time I stayed there, so I didn’t know. 
For the room it’s average. Clean but the linen is little bit dark and a lot of spot.
First day I got breakfast, the breakfast is fine and no one ask for bfast voucher (they even didn’t give me voucher when check in). Second day, they ask for bfast voucher. Please if you work at hospitality consistent rule is a must!!!!
If you want to request late check out you must pay 50.000rp.
This hotel is at a strategic place. It’s located near 3 big mall in kelapa gading like MOI, MAG and MKG.
I need 1,5 hrs to reach airport(out of peak hours). 
For me this hotel is affordable and good for a short business trip around kelapa gading or pulo gadung.

text:
The good:
1. Room size is fairly nice.
2. Bedding is good

The 'meh':
1. It's evident they try hard to make a unique room layout, but the end result is awkward. Having a sink located on the other side from the bathroom is not creative. It's annoying.
2. Rp. 100,000 CASH deposit at check-in? 

The bad:
1. There's no instruction how to call the operator from the room phone. How on earth first time guests would know to dial 8 to reach front desk? What happens in the event of an emergency?
2. Noise insulation. Although the tiny window in my room overlooks a void, which typically means no street noise, my room has a connecting door that just happens to have a neighbor that woke up at 5AM and started packing and chatting. It didn't help that the previous evening some parents let their young kid scream and run across the corridor repeatedly.
3. At breakfast, I was asked to pay Rp. 51,000. Apparently it's not possible to charge the breakfast bill to the room. When I asked to be presented a bill first, the waiter handed me a 'temporary invoice' in the amount of Rp. 62,000.
title: Decent

text: This hotel is very recomended for travellers who is looking for a clean and comfortable hotel in north jakarta..try it and you won' t be regret..very strategic location,you can get anywhere in kelapa gading with easyway cos they provide the shuttle bus for the nearest mall..the helpfull employee also make my stay in bnb feel perfect..
title: I' ll be back...

text: Was on a business trip, so didn't really care about anything else. Location quite strategic for those who like shopping. Easy to get taxi to go out. The room and hotel in general quite clean. Service was so so but staffs were polite. Breakfast also above average. Overall a great experience.
title: Great budget experience

text: Try this hotel the first time after a disappointing time at whiz kelapa gading. The staff are friendly. Quick checkin. The deposit has to be done in cash because they don't have the machine. The room is clean. The wall at the room is a bit too thin. Thats why I gave it four star not five. But overall a pleasant stay.
title: Pleasant stay at bnb

text: I stayed here for 2 night. The hotel is clean, room and lobby. Nice interior design, colourfull :). Good service, Very good location, near with 3 big malls; Mall of Indonesia, Mall Kelapa Gading and Mall Artha Gading, and many restaurant around kelapa gading area, from street food to 5 star restaurant. Room size is also not too small, not like other budget hotel. But I don't like the location of washbasin, because they place it outside the bathroom. The breakfast was ok, but it would be better if they also provide omelette/fried egg and toaster. I recommended this hotel if you just for bed and breakfast.
title: Clean budget hotel....

text:
I stayed on Friday, January 24 because i will have graduation ceremony on 25.
I decided to stayed at this hotel because its cheap but still have good service.
Its near kelapa gading mall and mall of indonesia, its about 15 minutes with taxi.
Its easy to get taxi from this hotel because they always standby taxi.
title: Good location and good price

text:
We booked this at the last minute for the final 5 nights of our stay and we're SO glad that we did! It's right near Kelapa Gading Mall, Mall Artha Gading and a few minutes from Mall of Indonesia. There's also a Lotte Mart just up the road.

The hotel is very new and has a really cool look about it. The room Was spacious and well appointe, the bed was exceptionally comfortable. The bathroom was cool, with glass walls on the shower, and there were all the amenities we require in a room. The hotel was also quiet and they have a small cafe onsite from where you can order basic cafe food to be delivered to your room, and also with great coffe and frozen drinks. We had the nasi goreng (excellent) and the club sandwich (not to our taste). The breakfast is basic, but there's fruit, bread, coffee, tea and some basic hot food.

We were very impressed with the front desk and concierge staff. The front desk staff booked us a taxi for the day of our departure and helped us to locate various items we needed to buy.

We would certainly stay there again if we could get it for the same price.
title: Amazing value for only - modern and funky.

text:
Really value for money.
Good Rooms for the price. Love the b'fast rest which is just beside the Coffee shop.
However, my room was floating just when im finished my shower.The shower drain is stuck. It was floating event to the outside of the rooms.

All services are good. 
Worth it for BNB class accommodation.

Welldone..!
title: Good Price

text:
it already started all wrong, I made a booking , wanted to change it and they had this strange no refund/amend policy although I wanted to change it more than a week before arrival. It seems they need this kind of money from people who change their minds but can not or are to lazy to contact/call the hotel themselves. On arrival they made me sign a stupid agreement that I would have to pay a Rp. 1mio penalty if I got caught smoking in the room. I mean they could have even asked if I am smoker or not. 
The room: First impression, great. Clean spacious, good. at a closer look it began all to fade. Sink had problems, tv channels all blurry, toilet is so close to the wall you can bang your head on it. Hot and cold water in the shower are unable to be mixed, you have to boil yourself or shower cold. Even worse: Breakfast, its a disaster, I am not spoiled but its uneatable. 
When checking out I asked them to call a taxi, but they only call the extra expensive type which they seem working together with. If you ask for another , they don't help you out. 

The Area is not friendly. nothing in walking distance beside dubious night clubs and plenty of them. Dirty canalization right in front is the only thing you find. At nights its kind of scary to walk around there, Briefly it was a disaster from A to Z, never recommend anyone to stay here. there are plenty of  better, cheaper hotels in Kelapa Gading.
title: disappointing

text: for the 3rd time I am stay at B n B hotel Kelapa Gading. I like this hotel. very clean and clear. make me comfortable. good Lobby , good staff. (But shower in the bathroom "hot water and Cold water don't have good function : Water sometimes cold and warm) . Breakfast also depleted and lack of preparation.
title: LIKE B n B hotel kelapa gading

text:

title: A good buget hotel

text: I found this hotel in internet when i was looking for a hotel for my business trip. Pictures of this hotel is very good & looks so clean. When i arrived in there, i was surprised that this hotel is better than in pictures. So clean & good ambience. I will come to this hotel again whenever i go to jakarta. title: Amazing!!!

text: I found this place on the internet and got interested because of the price. And also because this place is new and from the photos it got minimalist style. So i booked urban room for 1 night with a very affordable price(rp.350k). This hotel is located in kelapa gading. I would saythat it got a nice location because it got plenty of food stalls and nearmall of indonesia, and near tolls. When i first got here i like the interior,its all very trendy,urban,and minimalist even though its small. The room is clean, bright,and got a very nice atmosphere. I feel comfortablr stayig there. One of the cons would be the breakfast buffet, it didnt have plenty selection, and it didnt really manage well. I have to wait a bit long for the staffs to refill the food and drinks. But overall is a nice hotel, would definetly recommend this for people with low budget that wants to sleep well and comfortable.
title: Fits the budget

text: A new hotel with minimalis design. The room is clean and comfortable. The reception and the housekeeper are friendly and quick response to our need as we bring our 3 months baby there. Can ask for hot water at the coffee shop. The breakfast really standart and when you got late for breanfast then you'll get nothing to eat.
title: Nice hotel

text:
At first i didn't expect much of this hotel - but then surprisingly this is actually a good hotel.

When i came there's a bit of unpleasant things happens in the receptions area, which is after twice confirming about my room - i ask for one single bed but they said it was twin. I refuse, and then they make me wait a bit because the room is not ready, i arrive at the hotel around 17:30 and my room is not ready... hmmm that's 2 unpleasant things happens in a row, specially when you just got to the hotel and all you want is to get some rest after your trip.

So after about 15 minutes - they give me my room and upgrade it to urban deluxe, i thank you for the gesture. So i went to my room... come to my surprise that the room is very well design, it's not mainstream but yet comfortable. It can even fit for 3 people - even if one have to stay in the sofabed. The room is quite spacy and the water in the shower is just right (right temperature and right pressure). Nice room for the price that they offer.

It was a good sleep - all noise didn't come in to the room.
To find a restaurant you have to walk around 10-15 minutes to the nearest one - and yes it is dark at night so better to use a vehicles. But there is so much good food around BNB (kelapa gading area) so if you like food hunt this hotel can be your place.
IT's also near to go to Mall Of Indonesia (but i suggest you took a car / motorcycle) specially during the night. Also there was a reflexology / massage place nearby.

Breakfast time is quite crowdy and the food is so so but i didn't complain much since this is a budget hotel - you can find a lot of good food around kelapa gading area anyway.
They also have "KAFFEIN" coffee shop just near the breakfast place - they provide decent cup of coffee even if the price isn't that competitive (caused of the "just another coffee" style - nothing special)

Overall the stay here is surprisingly good - they offer a good price for walk in customer also.
If you stay alone - it's okay to book the urban standard room but if you are with someone or you family - i recommend that you took the urban deluxe
title: Surprisingly refreshing

text: First i knew BnB Hotel jakarta Kelapa Gading from one website that i always find for new hotel and good price. i think that i like to try for new hotel in JKT and the price are very competitive. Nice front desk that i meet first. Than i get upgrade room because STD room are fully that day. Wow I appreciate it. Very kindly Front desk agent ^^ . But all room can't smoke (poor me). i must go down to lobby just for smoking.. Never mind because that's the rule from the others hotel. One the most important that i love that room. very clear and clean. And for the last, i dissapointed with greeter/waitres when Breakfast. not kindly and i know that's to hectic. still need learn to services the guest and better conversation.
title: Good B&B Hotel Jakarta

text: Stayed there 1 night, the hotel is new, so it is very clean and neat. The room is nice but nothing special there. The breakfast has very few choices, only rice, fried noodles, egg, chicken curry, and vegetables. The design of the bathroom isn't comfortable for me and the shower sometimes hot, sometimes cold though i didn't change the tap. location pretty good, near to MOI and kelapa gading mall. Free parking for guest.
title: New and clean hotel

text:
I checked in in this hotel when they just opened in end of June. The hotel was not bad, but also there was  not outstanding as people said in other online reviews.

This hotel not really closed with the mall as they said, especially if you not bring the vehicles. The closest big mall, Mall of Indonesia can be reached around 10-15 minutes by walking, and the surrounding area very dark and tranquil, I am afraid that muggers and purse snatchers appears in the middle. To reach the biggest and nicest mall in Kelapa Gading, Mall Kelapa Gading and La Piazza, you must need taxi or if you walk, it takes almost 30 minutes. There are good hotels nearer than this hotel such as Harris Hotel or the new one, Fave Hotel. 

The facilites just so-so, wi-fi in lobby area and the room worked well, sometimes drop down, but did not matter as long as you just use your gadget only for checking your email (note: probably because this hotel not really full occupied, if it is, may be it get worse). 

In the room, you just only get very very tiny 3 in 1 soap, which wasn't cover even only 1x shower. Bedroom and bathroom were clean and new, but the bed is not really good, it was quite hard, and I cannot sleep well. TV channels also not many choices, I have stayed at other budget hotels and they provide many international and local almost 50 channels.

Next morning, I came down with my wife to get breakfast. I had craved that the breakfast will be good since the cafe was good ambient. But, it wasn't materialized (poor me). We only have 3 choices; nasi lemak, fruit salad, and eggplant sautee and you may choose one. I have chosen nasi lemak and my wife took eggplant sautee with sunny side up, and they deliver to my table with cold and tasteless condition. When I asked to get all of the choices, the waiter only said can not, that was the package and they were budget hotel. I have stayed in many budget hotel, and they still can provide simple and nice buffet. 

There was no problem upon check out, but it seems there are many others lower star budget hotel but had better facilities and services.
title: not bad hotel, but unforgettable...

text: Un plaisir de séjourné dans cet hôtel. Personnel au petit soin, on se sens comme à la maison. Le wifi fonctionne très bien, il y a une supérette ouvert 24/24, et ils fournissent tout ce dont vous avez besoin à la demande.

text:
翌日からメリディアンに泊まる前に、単発ステイとして泊まりました。

東ジャカルタにあるため立地としては中心部から離れていますが、ホテルとしては比較的満足でした。

ホテルの周りには何もないため、ホテルロビーにあるコンビニか5分ほど歩いた先にロッテマートや、韓国系の料理屋もありました。両替所が近くなく、20分くらい歩いた先にあったので、空港から直接来る場合は、両替しておくと良いでしょう。

トイレはウォシュレット付きなのが特に良かったです。
title: 単発ステイ

text:
Hôtel assez récent semblable à un Ibis ou Formule 1.
Chambre fonctionnelle avec douche et WC, lavabo dans l'entrée, petite fenêtre, Air conditionné, TV.
Wifi gratuit mais signal faible.
Accueil cordial et bienveillant à la réception, le personnel est poli, gentil.
Petit déjeuner inclus à la Cafétaria du rez de chaussée : correct.
La maintenance n'est pas au top : la porte d'entrée de la chambre est sale, avec des traces multiples et aussi sur les murs à l'intérieur : il est vrai que la peinture est blanche, mais la première impression est désagréable. Un nettoyage quotidien ou des retouches de peinture réguliers éviteraient ses dégradations. La vitre de la fenêtre présentait également un niveau insuffisant de propreté. C'est bien dommage !
Sinon, on se trouve dans un quartier moderne avec des centres commerciaux mais dans l'avenue principale qui n'est pas celle de l'hôtel.
Attention : depuis l'aéroport bien préparer le plan et l'adresse précise de l'hôtel pas facile à trouver : dans mon cas le chauffeur s'est arrêté 4 fois pour demander son chemin. 
L'hôtel est à environ 45 minutes de l'aéroport. Il y a toujours des taxis devant l'hôtel, il faut compter environ 150 000 IDR.
En résumé : rapport qualité-prix correct pour un court séjour et juste dormir.
title: Pratique pour un transit à Jakarta

text:
Отель новый и это его главное достоинство. Номера маленькие, нет ни шкафа ни холодильника, но кондиционер работает отлично и душ большой и чистый.
     Персонал дружелюбный.
От центра на такси минут 30 ехать, 8$ поездка. Рядом расположен огромный торговы центр.
Вообщем отель для тех, кому нужно переночевать недорого в этом районе.
title: Очень свежий бюджетный отель

text:
